a cartoonist

What did she feel insecure about?
her storylines

I mainly create my work for newspapers and magazines, 
even though plenty of my fellow artists have moved to the film industry. 
I guess I enjoy seeing my characters on paper. 
While I've always been proud of my drawing skills, 
I used to doubt my storytelling abilities all the time, 
but now I'm genuinely happy with how my stories develop and 
how complex my characters are.

